      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of June 18 roundup of experts' view on revitalizing Procter &amp; Gamble; Ivory soap was invented in 1878, and Tide detergent was introduced in 1946 (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A roundup last Sunday of the views of a variety of experts for revitalizing Procter &amp; Gamble misstated the history of two of the company's products. Ivory soap was invented in 1878, not in the 1920's; Tide detergent was introduced in 1946, not 1938.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
